<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terms and Conditions - Blood Donation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to your existing CSS file -->
    <style>
        /* Additional styles specific to the terms page */
        body {
            background-color: #f2f2f2; /* Light background for the body */
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif; /* Consistent font family */
        }

        .terms-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 350px; /* Same width as login and registration containers */
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #c21325; /* Updated red color for heading */
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }

        ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        a {
            color: #c21325; /* Consistent link color */
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline; /* Underline on hover for links */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="terms-container">
        <h2>Terms and Conditions for Blood Donation</h2>
        <p>Please read the following terms and conditions carefully before donating blood:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Eligibility Criteria:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Donors must be at least 18 years old (16 or 17 with parental consent).</li>
                    <li>Must weigh at least 110 pounds (50 kg).</li>
                    <li>Should be in good health and free from infections.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Medical History:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Provide a detailed medical history.</li>
                    <li>Individuals with certain high-risk behaviors may be deferred.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Consent:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Donors must provide informed consent before donating.</li>
                    <li>Right to withdraw consent at any time.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Health Screening:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>A health screening questionnaire and physical examination will be conducted.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Post-Donation Care:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Donors should hydrate and rest after donation.</li>
                    <li>Avoid strenuous activities for a few hours post-donation.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Personal information will be kept confidential.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Donation Frequency:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Whole blood donation is typically allowed every 8 weeks.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Legal Liability:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>The blood bank is not liable for adverse reactions arising from donations.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us.</p>
        <a href="/registrationpage">Back to Registration</a> <!-- Link back to registration page -->
    </div>
</body>
</html>


